column2: SELECT TOP #  g.lgm_tot_p5#, p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r,  s.z as redshift, p.fracDev_r,  Z.p_cs_debiased, Z.p_el_debiased  Z.spiral, Z.elliptical, Z.uncertain FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecExtra AS g ON g.specobjid = s.specobjid  JOIN zooSpec AS Z ON Z.specobjid = s.specobjid WHERE   s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND g.lgm_tot_p5# >= #  AND p.devRadErr_r > #  AND p.devRad_r >= #  AND p.fracDev_r BETWEEN # AND #  AND Z.p_cs_debiased <= #  AND z.elliptical = #  AND s.class = &&&
